  "rules": {
    "background": "Use the Light asset on light backgrounds and the Dark asset on dark backgrounds. Dark brand surfaces use #21005E (headers, footers, in-app bar, email, merch, slide decks). The splash screen uses Secondary #F3EAFF.",
    "gradients": "Never use a gradient that is not brand-provided. Only two gradients are approved: (1) the main-logo swoosh gradient built into the gradient wordmark, and (2) the social-avatar tile gradient #ECEBFB to #F6E9F4.",
    "framing": "Long banners must give the logo generous padding — never frame the wordmark close to the edges.",
    "distortion": "Never stretch, rotate, recolour, fade, or add effects to the logo. Use it at full strength.",
    "hierarchy": "The gradient main logo is the primary mark — the default anywhere the brand should shine. The flat main logo is the secondary fallback for small sizes, limited-colour reproduction, and busy backgrounds. The M letterform is restricted to merch and in-app animation. The monogram (M in pill) is restricted to merch, small-scale uses such as name cards, and watermarks. Neither the M nor the monogram ever replaces the main logo in marketing or documents."
  },
